libmbus
------------------------------------------
libmbus is an open source library for the M-bus (Meter-Bus) protocol.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  cygwin-devel-3.6.1-1
  libmbus-devel-0.9.0+git20250205-1bl1
  libmbus0-0.9.0+git20250205-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.44-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/rscada/libmbus

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/rscada/libmbus.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libmbus-0.9.0+git20250205-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libmbus-0.9.0+git20250205-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libmbus-0.9.0+git20250205-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmbus-0.9.0+git20250205-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmbus0-0.9.0+git20250205-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmbus-devel-0.9.0+git20250205-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

